      	<h4>Corporate Overview</h4>
          <p>PyMPSA is a company within PiSA Group, LEADER in the pharmaceutical industry, engaged in the development and manufacturing of components and high quality medical equipment with over 25 years of experience in Mexico and throughout the world.</p>
          <p>PiSA GROUP is a 100% Mexican pharmaceutical company that emerged in 1945. PiSA Pharmaceutical has 7 manufacturing plants with over 14,000 employees allowing us to offer more than 1,000 pharmaceutical products and 3 affiliated plants to manufacture medical devices, veterinary products, gauze and surgical drapes.</p>
          <p>Currently, the list of our major clients include international companies such as Baxter, Bayer and Carefusion, as well as Mexican government institutes such as IMSS (Mexican Institute of Social Security) that gives medical attention to over 59 million affiliates and the ISSSTE (Institute of Security and Social Services for State Workers) which gives medical attention to more than 13 million Mexicans.</p>
          <p>PyMPSA currently has presence in over 20 countries in Central America, South America, The Caribbean, Europe, Middle East, and also in United States, through the exportation of own products, manufacturing of products to third parties with own brand and “tailor made” products (OEM Original Equipment Manufacturer) for various companies.</p>
          <p>We have more than 5.93 acres of modern and spacious facilities including 8 clean rooms for the manufacture of products class 10,000 and 100,000 with all the services and controls required such as air filtration, positive pressure, temperature and humidity control, strict access procedures, cleaning and sanitization, all under a monitoring and control system.</p>
          <h4>Our Procedures</h4>
          <p>PyMPSA has automatic machinery and equipment with the newest technology for the processes of extrusion, injection, stamping, assembly, packaging, sterilization, measurement and testing of products; all that in addition to the design and development of our products.</p>
          <h4>Mission</h4>
          <p>We are a manufacturing company of medical devices, focused on fulfilling with discipline the expectations of customers through quality and timely delivery of our products, supporting our operation with certified staff, cutting edge technology and an agile and effective administration, achieving the expected profitability of the company.</p>
          <h4>Vision</h4>
          <p>"Being recognized as the world class leader manufacturing company of medical devices in the Americas.”</p>
          <h4>Our People:</h4>
          <p>PyMPSA has over 1,300 professionals across 8 production chains committed to excellence and aware that each of their actions work in favor of life.</p>
          <h4>Certifications, Registrations and Distinctions</h4>
