          <h4>Our Products</h4>
          <p>PyMPSA has a wide range of products that include: infusion equipment, Burette equipment, 3- way stopcock Extension, urine bags, parenteral and enteral nutrition bags, peritoneal dialysis bags, and Hemoline epidural equipment.</p>
          <h4>Experience with Continuous Improvement</h4>
          <p>Since 2009 PyMPSA has incorporated the working philosophy "Lean Six Sigma," developing improvement techniques such as Hoshin Kanri, VSM, Kaizen Teian, Kaizen, TPM and Six Sigma Improvement Projects.</p>
